title: Cat Adorably Mumbles To Himself While Watching Birds On Patio
text:
Cat Adorably Mumbles To Himself While Watching Birds On Patio   
Charlie is a cat that likes to talk to himself. He can’t help it, he just gets very excited when watching and stalking the birds that appear outside on the patio from inside his home. 
Share Charlie’s antics with your friends and family.
